text: Ne olwakhwakhuboolela mbu: “Toto Nyasaye wuwo amalile okhubotokhana Abandu abo.” Ne shikhwakhola amaloro kalia akakhwakhwechesia halali okhutema Abandu.	(Nende okhurumbulwa) mukurani omusala okwashienwa kulia, akwakhwakhwechesia. Ne khubekanyilisinjia halali shikabametanga shosi shosi tawe halali obukori obukhongo
